# Script Rules

- Build and playtest scripts are part of the developer workflow contract.
- `scripts/build-app.mjs` controls fallback bundle order. Keep it accurate.
- Screenshot and harness scripts should remain deterministic and safe to rerun.
- When changing file paths, selectors, or output locations, update the affected script in the same change.
